title: Season 1 Trailer
itunes:title: Teaser Trailer in the trailer...it's a teaser...in the trailer
description:
Welcome to our debut! Introducing...Psychology of Nothing podcast!

Good news, we're getting the hang of things...ahem, recording, editing, publishing...and we have a trailer for you. Take a listen and learn about what you can expect in episodes to come. If you're curious and you want more, subscribe. If you subscribe now, you'll find our fist episode in your podcast house waiting for you when it drops. 

P.S. The first episode is all about underwear, yep...underwear.

 

Also, check out our podcast website: psychologyofnothing.com

 

Intro music notes: Sooner Or Later (The Spark That Thought Mix) by The Spark That Thought (c) copyright 2010 Licensed under a Creative Commons Noncommercial Sampling Plus license. http://dig.ccmixter.org/files/The_Spark_That_Thought/29810
